model.metaheuristic.problem

Interface Problem<S extends Solution<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - Type of solution
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PipeOptimizing, VanzylOriginal

    public interface Problem<S extends Solution<?>>
    Class that denote a problem.

    If the problem open a resource override the close method to close its. Notes:

    For developer: If you implement a function that call closeResources() be careful not to close epanet until the experiment is finished, otherwise the program will close not show any warning error. This is probably due to a problem in epanet dll library.

      • applySolutionToNetwork

        @Nullable
default @Nullable Network applySolutionToNetwork(Network network,
                                                            Solution<?> solution)
        Apply the solution to the network.

        Notes:
        This method is used to save the solution as a inp from the ResultWindow. Return null if you don't want use this method, i.e, you don't want save solution in inp for a problem.
        Parameters:
        network - a copy of the network instance opened configured with inp setting up.
        solution - the solution to be setting in the network. It solution is the same type of S, so you can cast it.
        Returns:
        the network received and modified or null.
